  * Demonstrated experience in System Administration and support. 
  * Broad exposure to a range of IT systems, APPs, software, and solutions. 
  * Experience in the support of PCs, operating systems, applications, network, and communication technologies. 
  * Sharing of workloads, collectively solving problems, and supporting other team members with the management of projects. 
  * Ability to communicate and build relationships at all levels. 
  * Work autonomously, plan and organize to a high standard. 
  * Relevant qualifications in IT, Computer Science, or relevant field highly desirable 

